* Steps to add spring devtools:
1) Add below dependency to pom.xml:
<dependency>
			<groupId>org.springframework.boot</groupId>
			<artifactId>spring-boot-devtools</artifactId>
			<scope>runtime</scope>
			<optional>true</optional>
		</dependency>
2) If working on intellij 2021 and after enable below settings:
File-->Settings-->Advanced Settings--> Allow auto make to start even if deployed application currently running